item.description: Just throwing this out there, doesn't need t to be a formal meetup, if you are looking for a fun place for karaoke, not a lot of attitude just good, back to basics karaoke then Join DJ Jodi or DJ Dave each Friday night at 9pm at Josie's Place in Everett. If you are just looking for a basic karaoke joint, no frills, great song selection, neighborhood joint, with character and a few characters too, then this is the place. It's a small little neighborhood bar, that gets a good little cross section of patrons, but not a lot of karaoke singers, so if you like to sing and want an audience that appreciates your talents, then give Josie's a try. No long rotations, and you will sing multiple times. We have a great song selection, and we can make most anyone anyone sound good. Friendly and fun place to hang out. Hope to hear from you.
item.name: Friday Night Karaoke @ Josies Place Everett
